# HOW TO GET YOUR APP PASSWORD (free, takes ~2 minutes):
#
#  1. Go to: https://myaccount.google.com/security
#  2. Under "How you sign in to Google", click 2-Step Verification → Turn it ON
#  3. Go back to Security page, scroll to "App Passwords" (search for it if hidden)
